Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.00,Ep_Title,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,240)\fnArial}Q: {\fn}What do you think of {\fnArial}Satoru Gojo{\fn}?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.16,0:00:05.36,Flashback,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,He's a teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.80,0:00:10.09,Flashback,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,And without him, I would have been \Nexecuted by now, so he's also—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.09,0:00:11.99,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Technically, he's my benefactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.29,0:00:13.42,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Technically.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.42,0:00:16.56,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,That also goes for other \Npeople, too, not just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:20.67,Flashback,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I don't know him all that well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.67,0:00:22.93,Flashback,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,But there's one thing I can say for certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:23.99,Flashback,Maki,0000,0000,0000,,He's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.99,0:00:24.91,Flashback,Panda,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.91,0:00:25.89,Flashback,Toge,0000,0000,0000,,Salmon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:27.56,Flashback,Maki,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:29.98,Flashback,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,He's flippant. Egotistical.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:31.86,Flashback,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,And it goes without saying, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:33.93,Flashback,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,He's the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.61,0:01:11.12,Show_Title,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,825)\pos(320,10)\3c&H8ECEDD&}JUJUTSU KAISEN\N{\fs16\bord0\fscy100\c&HDEDCE0&}Shibuya Incident
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:29.02,Ep_Title,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 33\N{\fs30\fscy150}Shibuya Incident - Gate, Open
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:37.01,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, weed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.97,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,This is the third time we've met, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:43.24,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,And you still underestimate \Nthe hell out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:45.33,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:49.92,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:51.50,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:53.59,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones who said
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:02:56.85,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,not to run, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:08.85,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Did he just touch—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.11,0:03:28.49,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:37.13,Italics,Hanami,0000,0000,0000,,He's only targeting Jogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:48.67,Italics,Hanami,0000,0000,0000,,So his earlier declaration \Nwas just misdirection?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:50.36,Italics,Hanami,0000,0000,0000,,He's also...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:57.57,Italics,Hanami,0000,0000,0000,,stopped using his Limitless technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:00.87,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:03.58,Italics,Hanami,0000,0000,0000,,He's given up on adjusting his technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:06.32,Italics,Hanami,0000,0000,0000,,and started focusing on \Ncompact attacks using
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:10.04,Italics,Hanami,0000,0000,0000,,cursed energy manipulation in this \Nspace that's filling up with humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:19.81,Italics,Hanami,0000,0000,0000,,However, that means there's \Nno need to slip into the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:23.75,Italics,Hanami,0000,0000,0000,,I can just use my technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:32.35,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't dismiss Domain Amplification, Hanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:41.61,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,This is where you're weak, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:46.92,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:50.37,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use Domain Amplification and \Nyour Innate Technique at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:54.85,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,I remained safe only because I used \NDomain Amplification to protect myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:58.50,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,He's operating at this level with only basic \Ncursed energy manipulation and martial arts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:02.96,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru Gojo,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:06.26,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,what is there that you're {\i0}not{\i1} capable of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:10.18,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:12.25,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,He's not a cursed spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:14.89,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he's one of the incarnated \NDeath Painting Wombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:16.77,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,He's annoying, but he comes later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:21.67,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:26.49,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,The more you try to neutralize my technique \Nwith your Domain Amplification,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:29.70,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,the stronger I have to maintain my technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:34.11,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think this asparagus has the \Nenergy left to withstand that, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:35.09,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:53.52,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru Gojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:54.73,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:11.25,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Hanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:22.52,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:25.63,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,The Prison Realm is a living barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.49,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,It's what Genshin was reduced to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:30.52,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing that cannot be \Nsealed in the Prison Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:35.97,Flashback,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Then of course there are conditions \Nto sealing something in it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.15,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,One minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:44.16,Flashback,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:46.95,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Once the Prison Realm's gate is opened,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:51.00,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,we'll have to keep Satoru Gojo \Nin its effective sealing range
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:54.45,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,of four meters for one whole minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:27.82,Flashback,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:31.13,Flashback,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll burn you to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:37.29,Flashback,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't join forces with us just to push \Nthat impossible task onto us, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:40.54,Flashback,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Even the lives of several \Nthousand ignorant humans
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:44.98,Flashback,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't be enough to warrant fighting \Nthat thing under those conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.85,Flashback,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,for a full minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:51.38,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting heated up, Jogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:53.37,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:55.46,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we do need a minute—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:27.74,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let Hanami's death be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:32.21,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Use the humans as cover, \Nand focus on hit-and-run tactics!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.18,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Choso!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:45.19,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not going to help, \NI'll kill you myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:50.28,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:56.77,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Not too close, not too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:58.77,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,But that's the best they can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:02.21,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,The people who can't see cursed \Nspirits have started avoiding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:05.17,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,If their numbers keep declining \Nand space opens up,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:07.37,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,then I can catch Volcano Head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:10.96,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,No more releasing my technique \Nto lure it in like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:14.75,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,I've revealed my goal of beating \Nthem to a pulp in close combat,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:17.20,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,and it'll be an issue if it keeps \Nits distance and coordinates with
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.80,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,that Death Painting to unleash \Na big attack through the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:25.28,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I can't save everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:32.23,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,So I promise to exorcise them instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.29,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,It's still not time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:37.23,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,It has to have been over \Ntwenty minutes by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:41.84,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:45.52,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru Gojo's still completely composed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:50.92,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,We need him much more on edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:53.93,Sign_Basic,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\b1\an8\c&H455051&\3c&HF1FFFF&\shad0}Meiji Shrine (Harajuku)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:06.11,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you oka—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:08.92,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone got turned into monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.93,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,and got on the train...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:17.80,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I... I was told I wasn't needed \Nbecause the train was full!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:22.87,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,So he was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:24.68,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:28.62,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:31.10,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,...got on the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:33.01,Italics,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}An eight-car train is pulling in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:36.45,Italics,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please wait behind the yellow line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:36.45,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Gojo-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:40.52,Italics,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please do not lean on the platform doors \Nor reach your hands or face past them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:48.83,Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,Train's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:50.73,Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,We're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:06.18,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:09.66,Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:11.68,Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:12.67,Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:14.64,Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,It's a train!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:15.82,Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:16.81,Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:17.52,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:18.35,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:18.97,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:20.17,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:51.23,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are they thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:55.49,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Jogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:01.68,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Man, the air smells so nice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:03.43,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,It's full of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:06.13,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave a few humans alive after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:08.93,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,We can release them into the woods \Non weekends and go hunting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:11.41,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Can I burn the forest down with them in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.21,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Hanami'll get mad over that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:15.90,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Hanami is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.81,0:12:18.93,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:18.98,Sign_Basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(375,0)\fnComic Sans MS\c&H090A13&\3c&HC7D0D9&\shad0\an8\b1\fs16\move(420,60,420,90,23,689)}What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:24.00,Show_Title,Eyecatch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1350,0)\1c&H75EFED&\3c&H75EFED&\blur20\1a&HE0&\3a&HC0&\pos(320,18)}JUJUTSU KAISEN
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:23.97,Show_Title,Eyecatch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1350,0)\1a&HFF&\3c&HC5E3EC&\pos(320,18)}JUJUTSU KAISEN
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.21,0:12:28.97,Show_Title,Eyecatch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(675,0)\3c&H1EDDF0&\pos(320,18)\c&H292619&}JUJUTSU KAISEN
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.16,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't hit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.33,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Patchface!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:50.41,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,The one Nanami and Yuji talked about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:01.55,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you one of the \Ngross things about humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:06.09,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:18.90,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,So there are either cursed spirits \Nor curse users above us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.23,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Blood Manipulation: Convergence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.23,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Idle Transfiguration: Soul Multiplicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:22.23,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Supernova.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:22.23,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Body Repel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:44.51,Italics,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru Gojo isn't like Yuji Itadori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:47.88,Italics,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,I know he's capable of cold logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:50.97,Italics,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,He probably assumes \Nsome degree of sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:54.22,Italics,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,is needed as he makes certain to exorcise us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:59.06,Italics,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,But with both the death count and \Nthe number of living people rising,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:03.40,Italics,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,the scales determining what degree \Nis acceptable can no longer function.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:07.61,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,What you need to do right now
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:11.41,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,is use your Infinite Void to \Nkill us and all the people here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:14.66,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,so you can save the people \Noutside of your domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:17.33,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,But you're incapable of doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.83,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Because the sacrifices \Nyou're willing to accept
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:22.54,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,are "people killed by cursed spirits,"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:26.67,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,not "people killed by Satoru Gojo."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:29.43,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Now, think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.47,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Ponder it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.85,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Focus your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:40.06,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:42.23,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Domain Expansion:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.03,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Infinite Void.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:20.73,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,It was a desperate gamble on a Domain \NExpansion lasting two tenths of a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:29.57,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Two tenths of a second was the limit \NSatoru Gojo set purely on instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.61,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,It was the amount of time he believed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:34.28,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,non-sorcerers could \Nwithstand being in Infinite Void
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:37.54,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,without becoming vegetables \Nor facing after-effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.13,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,During that two tenths of a second,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:52.13,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,roughly half a year's worth \Nof information flowed into
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:56.18,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,the brains of the non-sorcerers \Nand transfigured humans present,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:59.64,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,rendering every one of them \Nunconscious while standing upright.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:19.04,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,However, all the survivors from B5F
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:22.71,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,were able to return to \Nsociety two months later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:24.92,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,That's how limited his Infinite Void was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:41.18,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, that meant the special-grade \Ncursed spirits could reawaken at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:43.77,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,So, with their potential \Ncounterattack in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:47.27,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru Gojo narrowed his focus \Non the transfigured humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:14.88,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,After dismissing his domain, \Nthe strongest sorcerer of the modern age
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:19.80,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,slaughtered all of the roughly 1,000 \Ntransfigured humans unleashed upon B5F
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:24.10,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,in 299 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:00.68,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Prison Realm, Gate Open.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:08.23,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:10.98,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we do need a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:25.33,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:29.67,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:31.67,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:34.17,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.43,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,A fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:44.51,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,A transformation technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:49.31,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's really him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:04.74,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a minute in Satoru Gojo's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:14.71,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't lose yourself in thought
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:17.34,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,in the midst of battle, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:19.67,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sense any cursed energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:21.76,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get my body to move, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:23.76,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,This is checkmate, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:27.64,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,So, who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.39,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Suguru Geto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.81,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:34.11,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,How sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:36.73,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Your body, your cursed energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:40.95,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,All the information provided by these \Neyes is telling me you're Suguru Geto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:46.37,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:51.37,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,My soul is rejecting all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:53.21,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Now, answer me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.96,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:00.72,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:11.39,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,How could you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:15.83,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,That's my technique, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:19.86,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,I can pass from one body to another \Nby replacing its brain with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:23.36,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'm also able to use the \Ntechnique etched into the body I inhabit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:27.53,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted this man's curse \Nmanipulation and this situation, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:28.58,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:33.25,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Shoko Ieiri handle the disposal of \NSuguru Geto's body that day, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:39.88,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,That was an odd time for \Nyou to show consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:43.05,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to that, I was able \Nto obtain this body with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:47.22,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't worry. \NI'll release your seal eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:51.85,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred... no, maybe \Na thousand years from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:54.02,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,You're just too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:56.98,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,And you're in the way of my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:59.36,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:03.95,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it that beat the crap out \Nof that body before I killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:06.57,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta Okkotsu, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:10.83,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't see as much appeal \Nin that boy as you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:17.92,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Copying techniques without any conditions, \Nand a bottomless well of cursed energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:21.05,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Both of those were just effects obtained
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:24.22,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,from binding the soul of his \Nmost beloved with a pact.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.55,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:30.76,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,but Yuta Okkotsu can never replace you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:38.15,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight, Satoru Gojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:42.73,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet again in the new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:49.91,Main,Ui,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:52.70,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Something in my ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:55.41,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me, Yuji Itadori?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:56.21,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:21:58.71,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:00.75,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,Listen and understand the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:08.22,Italics,Mechamaru,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru Gojo has been sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.30,0:23:41.88,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of skin care?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.88,0:23:44.20,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're asking me that? Not that I mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.20,0:23:46.54,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,I do all kinds of things, but like, \Nit ultimately comes down to genetics.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.54,0:23:48.12,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure those with pale, smooth skin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.12,0:23:50.77,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,like Gojo-sensei would say, \N"I don't really do anything."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.77,0:23:51.76,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Pandemonium."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.78,0:23:54.99,Next_Ep_Title,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\blur4}Next Episode\N{\fs30\fscy150}Pandemonium
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.74,0:23:52.56,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you actually do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.56,0:23:53.36,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.36,0:23:54.71,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Grr!

